# Repo Explorer authenticates the Claude Agent SDK one of two ways — set exactly ONE.
# `pnpm launch` fills this in for you and lets you switch (re-run it, then restart the
# dev server). The app is local-only; the credential never leaves your machine.

# 1) Claude subscription (Pro/Max) — recommended; runs on your plan, not metered billing.
#    Mint a long-lived token with `claude setup-token`.
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# 2) Anthropic API key — pay-per-token. Get one at https://console.anthropic.com/.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: raises GitHub API rate limit from 60 to 5000/hr.
# Get a classic token at https://github.com/settings/tokens — no scopes needed for public repos.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=
